;;   ..................................................................
;;   ^       | Sets the instruction pointer (IP) direction to an upward
;;           | movement.
;;   ..................................................................
;;   v       | Sets the instruction pointer (IP) direction to a
;;           | downward movement.
;;   ..................................................................
;;   |       | Modifies the instruction pointer (IP) direction in a
;;           | horizontal mode:
;;           |   ----------------------------------
;;           |   Input direction | Output direction
;;           |   ----------------+-----------------
;;           |   down            | down
;;           |   ..................................
;;           |   left            | right
;;           |   ..................................
;;           |   right           | left
;;           |   ..................................
;;           |   up              | up
